Description: A Windows 11-like Wayland Desktop Environment
 LWinDesk is a lightweight Wayland desktop environment for Linux that
 provides a familiar Windows 11 experience. Features include a centered
 taskbar, start menu, snap layouts, virtual desktops, notification center,
 and quick settings panel.
